{"tid":1254112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用游蕙禎相做頭像  民建聯植潔鈴認衰稱搞錯","createTime":"2019-06-24T02:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T02:56:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0a4141aa78a99ffd1e412ef03c2cbb0d19aac1","tid":1254112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zdbVsE7AZ1.11Ox08FtNNQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-06/70e1cf70-9614-11e9-9bdb-45fc15125738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzdbVsE7AZ1.11Ox08FtNNQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-06%2F70e1cf70-9614-11e9-9bdb-45fc15125738&h=9507ddad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近愈嚟愈多人使用通訊軟件Telegram溝通，聲稱可以保密身份會更安全。因宣誓風波而被取消立法會議員資格嘅青年新政游蕙禎，今日(23日)傍晚喺社交網站上載一幅電話截圖，聲稱被東區建制派區議員植潔鈴盜用相片，指斥植企圖扮本土派，而植就向游認衰話搞錯，事後已即刻換相添！<br />\n<br />\n根據截圖，個人資訊頁面上寫住「民建聯 植潔鈴」，用戶名則為「@marychannn」同植潔鈴英文名Elaine完全唔同，惟最有趣係頭像卻係游蕙禎。游聲稱唔介意Elaine照住佢個樣整容，但塊面係佢嘅，質疑應該要問過佢先。東網記者嘗試聯絡Elaine至今未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n不過，游蕙禎及後再上載一段長約3分鐘嘅電話錄音，Elaine承認用錯相向游蕙禎認衰話唔好意思，解釋話唔想用自己個樣，喺軟件內搜尋見到「幾靚女」就用咗，有覺得似游蕙禎，但無核實，多次強調個電話係私人號碼，唔知點解游會得知。游蕙禎亦三番四次怒斥，話植無問過佢就亂用相，質疑係想扮本土派，無理由其他相唔用，偏偏揀中佢喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF-whats%E5%99%8F%E7%94%A8%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E7%9B%B8%E5%81%9A%E9%A0%AD%E5%83%8F-%E6%A4%8D%E6%BD%94%E9%88%B4%E8%AA%8D%E8%A1%B0%E7%A8%B1%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF-001032960.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF-whats%25E5%2599%258F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%2595%2599%25E7%25A6%258E%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2581%259A%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2583%258F-%25E6%25A4%258D%25E6%25BD%2594%25E9%2588%25B4%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A1%25B0%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2590%259E%25E9%258C%25AF-001032960.html&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=e83dde4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF-whats%E5%99%8F%E7%94%A8%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E7%9B%B8%E5%81%9A%E9%A0%AD%E5%83%8F-%E6%A4%8D%E6%BD%94%E9%88%B4%E8%AA%8D%E8%A1%B0%E7%A8%B1%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF-001032960.html</a>"}]}